default-wiki-text: This is a censorship resistant wiki, that stores the content on IPFS its state on the blockchain. If you are a token holder, you can edit it.
ipfs-not-connected: ⚠ Warning: IPFS is not connected to any peer. The content of your edits is not going to be propagated. Please, check your internet connection.
